// ==========================================
// SECTION: INFRAESTRUCTURA TÉCNICA (CORE)
// ==========================================
section(class="bg-surface-dark/40 border border-white/5 rounded-sm p-8 md:p-16 mb-24 relative overflow-hidden group")
  //- Efecto de iluminación sutil al fondo
  div(class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 size-96 bg-primary/5 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none")
  
  div(class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center relative z-10")

    //- Columna 1: Especificaciones
    div
      div(class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8")
        div(class="size-2 bg-primary animate-pulse shadow-[0_0_8px_#C9DA2B]")
        h2(class="font-display text-3xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white uppercase") 
          | Infraestructura 
          span(class="text-primary") Técnica

      div(class="space-y-10")
        //- Item 01
        div(class="flex gap-6 group/item")
          div(class="text-primary transition-transform group-hover/item:scale-110")
            span(class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl") network_check
          div
            h4(class="font-display font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white mb-2") Nodos Globales
            p(class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm") 
              | Servidores de ultra-baja latencia distribuidos estratégicamente en los principales puntos de intercambio de LATAM.

        //- Item 02
        div(class="flex gap-6 group/item")
          div(class="text-primary transition-transform group-hover/item:scale-110")
            span(class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl") security
          div
            h4(class="font-display font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white mb-2") Protección de Datos
            p(class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm") 
              | Encriptación de punto a punto (P2P) en cada descarga y transacción, asegurando la integridad de tu librería.

        //- Item 03
        div(class="flex gap-6 group/item")
          div(class="text-primary transition-transform group-hover/item:scale-110")
            span(class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl") analytics
          div
            h4(class="font-display font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white mb-2") Metadatos Extendidos
            p(class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm") 
              | Tracks analizados con precisión quirúrgica: BPM, Key y Cue Points listos para integración inmediata con Serato y Rekordbox.

    //- Columna 2: Visualizador Central (System Monitor)
    div(class="relative p-8 rounded-sm bg-black/40 border border-white/5")
      //- Decoración: Líneas de coordenadas
      div(class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none")
        div(class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-px bg-white/20")
        div(class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 w-px h-full bg-white/20")

      div(class="flex items-end justify-center gap-2 h-56 relative z-10")
        - const bars = [25, 50, 75, 100, 65, 85, 35, 80, 25, 45, 90]
        each h, i in bars
          div(
            class="w-3 bg-primary/20 rounded-t-sm relative group-hover:bg-primary/40 transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden" 
            style=`height: ${h}%`
          )
            //- Efecto de "escaneo" interno en las barras
            div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/60 animate-shimmer" style=`animation-delay: ${i * 0.1}s`)

      //- Icono Bolt Central con Glow
      div(class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center")
        div(class="text-primary opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity duration-700")
          span(class="material-symbols-outlined text-[160px] blur-sm") bolt